Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)\a6}製作 ？ 秋月暮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.03,0:01:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次殺人時 我還乳臭未干 留著鼻涕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.92,0:01:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想試試槍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fad(200,50)}五月7日 vale（葡語：山谷）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.93,0:01:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么要歇業啊？ Gyle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.72,0:01:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天我突然流下眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以再做1個人我就收山
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然完全不懂你說的是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.54,0:01:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的隱退比賽就由我來安排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼 我對看中的獵物從來只用1發子彈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.33,0:02:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 Gyle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.37,0:02:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 野蠻的脫獄犯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人渣警察
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.91,0:02:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蟑螂般生命力的Monstro的流氓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢耍老子的混蛋們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一個都無可挑剔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在什么地方？ 比如這個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四處亂竄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沿著331號公路 徑直北上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約后天會路過這一帶進入Aronpolis
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一個最有活力？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個家伙 難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副"我可以活著嗎"的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻自以為是、擅做主張
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.62,0:03:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種家伙 難道不該最先解決掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.31,0:03:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知死活的爆炸奔跑者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fad(200,60)}五月9日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里是003號車
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在331號公路上追捕通緝中的Michiko Malandro脫獄犯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標正在向Aronpolis方向逃竄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.21,0:03:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有越境的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里是本部 不允許超越管轄范圍的追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在越境前予以逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了逮捕 允許使用槍械
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死條子 煩死人了 你丫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是褐藻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開車窗 我要開槍了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 前面！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shinsuke 你丫想讓我等多久？ 啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 Satoshi君你聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拉了一團很大的便便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看嗎 非常大 我會送照片給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我猜猜看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅哩羅嗦 煩死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你這是什么口氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓Michiko帶槍的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那件事啊 你嚇了一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 你完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣嘛 你在生氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命生氣的Boss真是好嚴厲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾你的任務交給Gyle了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gyle 為什么 為什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我很嚴厲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什么！ 你搞什么！ 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.49,0:05:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爺真是危機萬分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么辦啊！ 喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先去道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 道歉了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 冒煙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是被女人甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨頭和心都一蹶不振了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.66,0:07:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是被稱為"村子的武士"的獵手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又知道我的什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.49,0:07:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未來不在這里 我注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰管你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有了錢 女人就會回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說你是這樣說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我要買下她的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不對女人和孩子下手！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是女人 這個家伙是你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.97,0:08:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你不想要？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不對女人和孩子下手...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是Satoshi Batista的代理人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著嗎 那個家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的家伙 你不怕這個家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好膽量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和你做個比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.05,0:09:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必客氣 覺得可以下手的時候就扣動扳機
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則 你會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子彈明天一早 會放在前臺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a3\fad(200,50)}五月10日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要賣廢品的話 我就收下了 100Arca
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等 你丫就沒有辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連話都不會說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 您有什么辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 看在你的面子上 就告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身邊的傻瓜的引擎已經不換不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我這里沒有備件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在鄰近的Corpo州 我兒子也在開店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以幫你們調貨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.27,0:10:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們著急要去Plano
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是鄰州 你丫就不能跑一趟？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我的腰非常痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.59,0:10:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能開車
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:10:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那么我去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便幫你按摩一下你丫老腰 怎么樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去跑一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.19,0:11:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么我要去給別人按摩腰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 Hatchin你要是不去做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就要負修理費 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個人是健康的 很健康
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 可別讓她逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑個屁啊 死老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 右
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 左
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 應該給Satoshi Batista打個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真幸運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的一見鐘情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我給你信號 然后你就減速
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在車身交錯的瞬間射殺對手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣一直開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里 死老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是女人 你是錢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akasha
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽延期 警察來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上車嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把這個給丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上車時給我一槍就不好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒能一槍搞定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 他是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么 為什么你丫會站在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死老頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:21:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什么 這算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
